    "description": "《夜血W：割喉之狼》是一款赛博朋克风格的动作角色扮演游戏，在这个充满未来科技与黑暗势力的架空世界中，您将扮演野心勃勃的帮派干部 洛雷托.古斯塔沃，您的目标是独自一人挑战并消灭叛变的弗雷帮以及找出帮派的叛徒，本作采用全新的操作系统，大幅度简化了游戏的操作，不需要复杂的操作即可畅快游玩，轻松享受动作游戏的快感，游戏采用了像素风格，拥有高速的动作节奏，其中创新的钩锁技能和简单而爽快的连招组合为玩家提供了丰富的战斗体验。此外，游戏还提供了简约但丰富的装备系统，让玩家能够根据自己的喜好来选择装备。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070450/extras/941579c71d13b9381c575bf7445a63dd.poster.avif?t=1749422609\" width=294 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070450/extras/941579c71d13b9381c575bf7445a63dd.webm?t=1749422609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070450/extras/941579c71d13b9381c575bf7445a63dd.mp4?t=1749422609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >连续迅速的普通攻击</h2><br>连续按鼠标左键，毫不留情的对敌人进行多段快速的攻击<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070450/extras/eb2d5766ad847660d2bcee4f8c3c1591.poster.avif?t=1749422609\" width=294 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070450/extras/eb2d5766ad847660d2bcee4f8c3c1591.webm?t=1749422609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070450/extras/eb2d5766ad847660d2bcee4f8c3c1591.mp4?t=1749422609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >钩锁位移攻击</h2><br>使用鼠标把准星对准敌人，然后按下右键进行使用索格斯突袭对敌人进行疾速追击。按住右键可以使用子弹时间，让您有更多的时间思考该去攻击哪个目标<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070450/extras/bbba2fc8e4c4fdafb08756d1e4af308b.poster.avif?t=1749422609\" width=294 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070450/extras/bbba2fc8e4c4fdafb08756d1e4af308b.webm?t=1749422609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070450/extras/bbba2fc8e4c4fdafb08756d1e4af308b.mp4?t=1749422609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >进阶攻击效果</h2><br>使用左键普通攻击3次，会积攒一次浮游剑追加攻击，然后按右键攻击敌人进行触发，效果分别有3种。您可以使用这种技巧对敌人进行额外攻击<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070450/extras/0211e9f2992015565cadb2949068bde4.poster.avif?t=1749422609\" width=294 height=232 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070450/extras/0211e9f2992015565cadb2949068bde4.webm?t=1749422609\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070450/extras/0211e9f2992015565cadb2949068bde4.mp4?t=1749422609\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >空中连击</h2><br>使用右键钩锁追击敌人后，衔接左键普通攻击对敌人进行畅快的空中连击<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3070450/extras/49c37a1ad79def6261a3211b4ee8207a.avif?t=1749422609\" width=294 height=232 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >主动装备槽</h2><br>主动装备槽位一共有2个，需要按P键打开背包把装备安装到相应的槽位中，初始的按键为Q键和E键。本游戏可以通过探索和挑战获得大量的装备来增强自身，使用不同的装备搭配出适合自己的战斗风格，另外设有2个被动装备槽，被动装备可以通过一些按键组合直接触发攻击效果",
